0.text: Chieng' winjo burano bende ema hulo tarik ma achijno yudoe ratiro mar ng'adone bura moruyore.

1.text: Momondo kawuono ni, yamo ne futo e ng'wech mar kilomita 83 kwom saa achiel, kendo ne igeno ni tekone dhi medo dok chien.

2.text: Fuoni maduong' matayo ringo mar remo en adundo, magoyo remo.

3.text: Websaitgii oseyudo jii maluwogii, ahinya to eweche somo.

4.text: Nengo mar dhi bayo yot koponi un ji mathoth, kaponi in kendi kata mana kod osiepni achiel tem umany jok mamoko mondo uchop jii ang'wen kata auchiel.

5.text: Kamera moko tiyo kod filim mar 6 kod 6 sentimeta, ahinya ahinya 56 kod 56 milimeta.

6.text: Los kendo ting' kopi meke chikeni gi gik yudo ja inshuaransni kodi.

7.text: Pong' odi gi kahawa mogundho e seche mag okinyi kendo gi chai mar chamomile matin makelo mor e seche mag otieno.

8.text: Kite madongo dongo mag baraf ma ridore e kor got ok gin gik malich miwuoro; kor got nyalo ting'o mana baraf mamol mos ahinya, to ka gimedore mokalore to giridore piny kaka kite mag baraf madongo dongo.

9.text: Ushuru mar msahara olos mopogre, epinje mopogore, kendo atamalo kaking'ade kod kiwango mar msahara migolee opogore, kowuok epiny moro nyaka machielo.
